cz.zcu.validator.jdparser.api.skeletons.modifiers

Class ModifierStatesUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.zcu.validator.jdparser.api.skeletons.modifiers.ModifierStatesUtil

  • public class ModifierStatesUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Design pattern - Library class. Util class for gathering modifiers from String. Every modifier (except access modifier - they have their gathering methods inside enum class) has here method for checking, if String contains it's String representation.
    Author:
    Stepan Cais, scais@kiv.zcu.cz, 5.12.2012
